About 88 Live Piano Bar
The hottest new venue!
88 Live Piano Bar features the finest musicians, vocalists, and special events.
We are a family-owned business, and we love live music. Bradentonâ€™s 5000 sq foot venue is classy and sassy. Bring your friends, loved ones in and enjoy a signature cocktail or something from our Italian kitchen. You are guaranteed to have a good time and make some lasting memories.
Fabulous Team
Partners Sherry, Scott & John welcome you to the Suncoastâ€™s premier live music venue!
Things are really hopping at 88 Live Piano Bar. Itâ€™s more than just a piano bar. Some of the best local musicians are performing there along with nationwide acts. We have comedy shows and all kinds of special events.
This music and entertainment venue is a happening place. It looks like a New York City nightclub inside that has a huge stage for the performers. There is a special VIP section for those who really want to go all out.
Hungry? Piano Bar 88 has great pizza and sandwiches. Cocktails? The bar is well stocked with your favorite beer and some of the best top-shelf liquor.
John Smith
General Manager
John Smith
is the General Manager with four decades of successful experience in restaurant and bar management. John specializes in community involvement to showcase his loyalty to schools, churches, athletic programs, and various other community activities. A strong believer in the power of positive thinking, John builds loyalty to his guests by knowing your name and treating you like family. John has been managing restaurants and bars for almost 40 years at some well-known establishments like Cracker Barrel, Longhorn Steakhouse, Hogs Breath Saloon and Fratellos.
